Package org.insa.graphs.model

Class Label

java.lang.Object
org.insa.graphs.model.Label
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Label>
Direct Known Subclasses:
LabelStar
public class Label
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Label>

Label class

This class is meant to implement the separation principle of the Djikstra algorithm by labeling the graph's nodes.
